#include<iostream>
#include<cstdio>
#define ulli unsigned long long int 
using namespace std;
ulli gcd(ulli a,ulli b)
{
	if(b==0)
	{
		return a;
	}
	else
	return gcd(b,a%b);
}
int main()
{
	ulli t;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--)
	{
		ulli n;
		cin>>n;
		ulli i,a,b;
		b=0;
		for(i=1;i<=n;i++)
		{
			cin>>a;
			b = gcd(a,b);
		}
		cout<<b<<"\n";
	}
}
